{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSToolBarTop","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Structure","modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"symbolKind":"struct","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents14OUDSToolBarTopV","title":"OUDSToolBarTop","platforms":[{"introducedAt":"15.0","deprecated":false,"beta":false,"unavailable":false,"name":"iOS"},{"introducedAt":"1.0","deprecated":false,"beta":false,"unavailable":false,"name":"visionOS"}],"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSToolBarTop","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSToolBarTop","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol"},"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI12ViewModifierP"],"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo"}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"The top toolbar (aka ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"navigation bar","type":"text"}]},{"text":" on iOS and iPadOS 18 and lower) sits at the top of the screen and provides contextual information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and controls related to the current view.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It typically displays the page title, and may include navigation actions such as “Back” or “Close” as well as supplementary actions.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It can contains leading and trailing actions.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSToolBarTop","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Overview","type":"heading","anc